Dialogue: 100,0:00:07.52,0:00:10.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，是时候隐藏起我的秘密身份了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, time to assume my secret identity.
Dialogue: 600,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.44,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}此处康妮的秘密身份隐藏方式与超人类似
Dialogue: 100,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}下周同一时间继续练习刀法吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Same time next week for sword training?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:12.46,0:00:15.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对啊，真可惜我不能在家继续练习\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah. It's a shame I can't practice more at home.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.60,0:00:17.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，等下！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, wait a sec. Hup!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:18.06,0:00:18.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}可以吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}May I?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:22.16,0:00:23.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}敬上\N{\fnArial\fs48}Here-eth.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:23.36,0:00:26.10,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}汝尽可使用吾母之刀\N{\fnArial\fs48}You can borrow-eth my mother's sword...Eth.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:26.48,0:00:30.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，你真是太好了，不过语法有点问题啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, that's so nice, if grammatically incorrect.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.84,0:00:35.19,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但汝不可赠吾与汝母之刀\N{\fnArial\fs48}But thou can't just givest me thine mother's sword.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.19,0:00:36.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}何不可？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why not-eth?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.16,0:00:39.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}皆因此刀之重要\N{\fnArial\fs48}Because it's really important-eth.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.44,0:00:42.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}此乃汝需持有之因\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's exactly why you should have-eth it.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:43.16,0:00:47.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}汝可在一周之内尽兴习刀\N{\fnArial\fs48}You can have all week to practice-eth with it-eth.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.04,0:00:50.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}感谢\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pbbhhthank you.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.14,0:00:54.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们得做好准备，如果我们要与孔雀石和橄榄石战斗的话\N{\fnArial\fs48}We got to be ready if we have to fight Malachite or Peridot
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.06,0:00:56.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当然还有那些怪异的宝石融合实验体\N{\fnArial\fs48}or those creepy gem-fusion experiments.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.96,0:00:58.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我会确保这把刀不出差错的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll make sure nothing happens to it.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那是车库门的声音！我妈回家了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's the garage door. Mom's home.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.66,0:01:03.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们必须得把刀藏起来\N{\fnArial\fs48}We have to hide the sword.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:03.76,0:01:06.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我妈不可能让我在家里放把刀的\N{\fnArial\fs48}There's no way mom would let me have this in the house.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:06.54,0:01:08.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}狮子？狮子?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Lion? Lion?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.56,0:01:09.39,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他溜走了\N{\fnArial\fs48}He walked off.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:09.76,0:01:11.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们该怎么办？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What are we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:14.62,0:01:17.98,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗨，妈妈，我在完成六点钟的小提琴练习\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hi, mom. Just finishing my 6:00 violin practice.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:17.98,0:01:19.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你五分钟前就该完成了\N{\fnArial\fs48}You should have finished five minutes ago.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.94,0:01:22.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你早该开始七点钟的自习了\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're late for your 7:00 study hour.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:22.48,0:01:23.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你好，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hello, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗨，莫雪伦医生\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hi, Dr. Maheshwaren.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:25.32,0:01:25.89,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你还好吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How are you?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:25.89,0:01:26.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}坐着\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sitting!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:28.36,0:01:29.52,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}今天工作并不轻松\N{\fnArial\fs48}I had a rough day at work,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.52,0:01:31.72,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我可不想碰到什么惊喜\N{\fnArial\fs48}and I'm not in the mood for any more surprises.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.08,0:01:33.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}医院发生了什么事？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What happened at work?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.72,0:01:36.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}今天遇到一件非常奇怪的事-\N{\fnArial\fs48}There was a really strange case at the hospital today --
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.06,0:01:39.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如同噩梦一般\N{\fnArial\fs48}straight out of a nightmare.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.00,0:01:41.52,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，不过别担心\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, don't worry.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.52,0:01:43.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}医患保密规则\N{\fnArial\fs48}The rules of doctor-patient confidentiality
Dialogue: 100,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.56,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不让我分享场面的细节，但-\N{\fnArial\fs48}keep me from sharing the graphic details, but --
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.36,0:01:49.18,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等下，我们什么时候有了个大衣架？\N{\fnArial\fs48}hang on a moment. When did we get a coat rack?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.66,0:01:50.98,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，不\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:51.28,0:01:52.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一把刀？\N{\fnArial\fs48}A sword?!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.02,0:01:54.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}康妮，你从哪里拿的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Connie, where did you get this?!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:55.24,0:01:55.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是-\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's --
Dialogue: 100,0:01:55.55,0:01:56.43,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我捡的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I found it.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:56.66,0:01:57.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我无意间在外面发现的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I just found it outside,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:57.96,0:01:59.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而我想给史蒂文看看\N{\fnArial\fs48}and I wanted to show it to Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你怎么能认为这是安全的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How could you possibly think this is okay? It's --
Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.94,0:02:05.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你知道每天我在医院里见到多少孩子\N{\fnArial\fs48}do you know how many children I see every day in the hospital
Dialogue: 100,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.45,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}因为玩刀而把自己脸切掉了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}who've cut their faces off playing with swords?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:08.62,0:02:08.98,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-\N{\fnArial\fs48}I --
Dialogue: 100,0:02:08.98,0:02:09.56,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}零！\N{\fnArial\fs48}none!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.74,0:02:12.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}因为他们都有关爱他们的父母\N{\fnArial\fs48}Because they all have parents who love them
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.00,0:02:14.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而父母们不会让孩子玩弄致命武器\N{\fnArial\fs48}and who don't let them play around with deadly weapons
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.46,0:02:16.52,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}搞得像混混一样！\N{\fnArial\fs48}like some kind of gang member!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.92,0:02:20.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不许摸刀-任何情况都不行！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No playing with swords under any circumstances.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:22.46,0:02:25.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我是莫雪伦医生，好的，冷静下，斯壮伯格\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is Dr. Maheshwaren. Yes, calm down, straumburg.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.97,0:02:27.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}又有一个？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Another one?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.44,0:02:27.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她会还回刀吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is she gonna give it back?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:27.80,0:02:29.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，我-我马上就过去\N{\fnArial\fs48}All right, I'll -- I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:30.10,0:02:31.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我必须得去医院了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I have to go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.64,0:02:32.74,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我会和你爸商量\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll have a talk with your father
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.74,0:02:34.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}算算你有多被禁足！\N{\fnArial\fs48}to calculate just how grounded you are.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:35.28,0:02:37.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且我们要用算盘！\N{\fnArial\fs48}And we're using the abacus.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.18,0:02:40.10,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我讨厌那个算盘\N{\fnArial\fs48}I hate that abacus.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.48,0:02:43.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，我太对不起了，她拿走了你母亲的刀\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, I'm so sorry. She took your mother's sword.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.92,0:02:45.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}也许我们能让她回心转意？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Maybe we can get her to change her mind.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.04,0:02:48.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她从不改变想法\N{\fnArial\fs48}She never, ever changes her mind.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:48.78,0:02:50.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们得靠自己拿回刀\N{\fnArial\fs48}We've got to get that sword back ourselves.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoa!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:54.98,0:02:55.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们不能把狮子带进去\N{\fnArial\fs48}We can't bring Lion inside.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:57.86,0:03:01.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果我妈把狮子也给没收了的话我会非常后悔的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'd feel really bad if my mom confiscated him, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.96,0:03:04.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，这没什么，他可以呆在这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, it's no problem. He can stay out here.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.56,0:03:07.74,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}听着，我总算找到了一个让他听从我的办法\N{\fnArial\fs48}Look -- I finally found a way to get him to do what I want.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.60,0:03:14.65,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}都不撕掉塑料包装\N{\fnArial\fs48}He didn't even take the plastic off.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.78,0:03:15.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}真是个禽兽啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}What an animal.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.45,0:03:19.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}打住，要严肃\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, serious.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.74,0:03:20.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对，要严肃\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah. Serious.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:23.82,0:03:24.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}This way.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.50,0:03:29.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊，你是指超级吓人的路\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ah, you mean the super scary way.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他们在晚餐后会将灯光调暗\N{\fnArial\fs48}They turn the lights down after dinner.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.76,0:03:33.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那是什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What was that?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:40.38,0:03:41.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}维斯特医生可不会喜欢的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dr. west ain't gonna like it.
Dialogue: 600,0:03:40.38,0:03:41.86,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}Dr.West致敬1985年的邪典片《活跳尸》
Dialogue: 100,0:03:42.14,0:03:44.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不过，维斯特医生可不在这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, Dr. west isn't here.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.44,0:03:56.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好的，好的，我刚到这里，嗯，嗯\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes, yes, I just got here. Mm-hmm. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你再说一下在哪找到他们的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Where did you say you found them?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.56,0:04:07.74,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}路边？\N{\fnArial\fs48}The side of the road?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.38,0:04:11.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我现在还不确定，毕竟还没亲眼见过\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm not sure just yet. I haven't had a look for myself.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.32,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这看起来可不像是车祸\N{\fnArial\fs48}It doesn't look like a car accident.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.62,0:04:18.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你没找到身份证件？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You didn't find an I.D.?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.36,0:04:21.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}听着，我会回电话的，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Listen, I'll call you back
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当，或者，我有问题的时候\N{\fnArial\fs48}when, or if, I have an answer for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.46,0:04:24.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}再见\N{\fnArial\fs48}Goodbye.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，现在\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, now.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:31.96,0:04:32.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她在做什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's she doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.22,0:04:35.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她很可能在检查体征\N{\fnArial\fs48}She's probably checking their vitals.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.26,0:04:37.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你之前就没见过医院吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Haven't you been to a hospital before?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:37.60,0:04:38.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没\N{\fnArial\fs48}No.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.72,0:04:39.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，算你走运\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh. Lucky.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.84,0:04:41.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，看\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, look.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.72,0:04:51.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没有心跳\N{\fnArial\fs48}No heartbeat.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，便宜的医院报销货\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh. Cheap hospital budgets.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.90,0:05:30.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}康妮！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Connie!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.68,0:05:31.98,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.22,0:05:35.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是怎么-你拿这个干嘛？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}How did you even -- what are you doing with this?!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.22,0:05:36.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我定了规矩-\N{\fnArial\fs48}I made a rule --
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}任何情况下都不能用刀\N{\fnArial\fs48}no swords under any circumstances.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.98,0:05:39.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但，母亲！\N{\fnArial\fs48}But, mom!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们回家再说\N{\fnArial\fs48}We will finish this conversation at home.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.16,0:05:49.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}先生？女士？维斯特先生？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sir? Ma'am? Dr. west?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.38,0:05:53.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他一天都不休息，不是吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}He can't take a day off, can he?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是你？这是我的另一位病人\N{\fnArial\fs48}You? It's my other patient.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你下床干什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}What are you doing out of bed?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么你没和斯壮伯格医生在一起？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why aren't you with Dr. straumburg?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.52,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那不是病人\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's not a patient.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.44,0:06:05.98,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不知道这里发生了什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't know what's going on here,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我会查个明白的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I am going to get to the bottom of it.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.62,0:06:19.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}康妮，我觉得那是宝石变异体\N{\fnArial\fs48}Connie, I think that's one of the gem mutants.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.82,0:06:21.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么？你确定？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}现在非常确定了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pretty sure at this point.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.78,0:06:27.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}母亲，我真的，真的，真的需要那把刀\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mom, I really, really, really need that sword.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.36,0:06:29.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}康妮，不，现在不是合适的时候\N{\fnArial\fs48}Connie, no. Now is not the time.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.76,0:06:35.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就是现在，母亲！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now is the perfect time, mom!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}康妮，你这是怎么了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Connie, what has gotten into you?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:37.98,0:06:41.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你知道我从不更改规矩的，小姑娘\N{\fnArial\fs48}You know I never go back on a rule, young lady.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:41.70,0:06:43.72,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}总得有点例外吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}There have to be some exceptions.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.72,0:06:47.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我又不是被规矩控制的机器人！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm not some rule-driven robot.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}康妮！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah! Connie!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.50,0:06:52.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}妈妈！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mom!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.64,0:06:53.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我来救你了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll save you!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.22,0:06:56.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}过来！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Here!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.96,0:07:03.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}把-你的-手-从我的康妮身上-拿开！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Keep your hands off my Connie!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这些患者真是不可理喻啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}These patients are beyond reason.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.02,0:07:10.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}母亲，只要你这次愿意改变你的规矩...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mom, if you would just go back on your rule this one time...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.44,0:07:16.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我只是需要帮助史蒂文并让我们逃离这里！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I just need to help Steven to get us out of here!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}母亲最了解！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mother knows best!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，快！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, come on!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:46.16,0:07:46.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.12,0:07:48.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们被困住了\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're trapped.
Dialogue: 600,0:07:47.12,0:07:48.06,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}此处"Dr. Gero, Patient 20"致敬龙珠Z中的格罗博士（人造人20号）
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.06,0:07:49.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们不必如此\N{\fnArial\fs48}We don't have to be.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.74,0:08:04.18,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}真的，妈妈，我知道该怎么做\N{\fnArial\fs48}Really, mom, I know how to do this.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.18,0:08:05.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，你不知道\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, you don't.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，她知道\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes, she does.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她一直在练习\N{\fnArial\fs48}She's been training.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她不是在随意玩弄那把刀\N{\fnArial\fs48}She wasn't playing around with that sword.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.74,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她在上课，学习如何正确使用它\N{\fnArial\fs48}She was taking classes, learning how to use it right.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.12,0:08:15.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}即使她一直在学习\N{\fnArial\fs48}Even though she's always studying
Dialogue: 600,0:08:14.12,0:08:15.62,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}宝石实验体的设计参考了《死亡空间》中的怪物，而右下的那只则和求生之路2里的Charger相似
Dialogue: 100,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}或者练习网球，或者做作业，\N{\fnArial\fs48}or practicing tennis or doing her homework,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.92,0:08:20.65,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她仍然在努力成为一名好的刀客\N{\fnArial\fs48}she still works really hard to be a good sword fighter.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.90,0:08:22.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，不不不不不不\N{\fnArial\fs48}No. No, no, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我了解我女儿\N{\fnArial\fs48}I know my daughter.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我知道她每一天每一秒都在做什么-\N{\fnArial\fs48}I know what she's doing every second of the day --
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.04,0:08:29.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她所有的活动，所有的网上交互\N{\fnArial\fs48}all her activities, all her internets.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.26,0:08:33.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我知道她不是某些玩刀的小混混！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I know she's definitely not some sword-fighting hooligan.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你一点都不了解我！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You don't know me at all!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.70,0:08:37.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你到现在还没注意到我的眼镜！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You still haven't even noticed my glasses.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.92,0:08:39.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你的眼镜有什么问题？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's wrong with your glasses?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.98,0:08:41.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}它都没有镜片了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}They don't have lenses anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.02,0:08:45.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我都快一年用不到真正的眼镜了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I haven't needed actual glasses for almost a year.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}怎么？你的视力突然被魔法治好了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What? Your eyesight just magically got better?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:48.94,0:08:49.98,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当然！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我一直在与魔法和怪物打交道\N{\fnArial\fs48}I've been dealing with magic and monsters
Dialogue: 600,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.92,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}康妮揭露秘密的情景和《野外怪家庭》类似——都是紧急关头不得不交代
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.92,0:08:55.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还有这种东西，从我认识史蒂文开始\N{\fnArial\fs48}and things like these since I met Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.88,0:08:59.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这也是为什么我需要你相信我知道该做什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's why I need you to believe I know what to do here.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.64,0:09:00.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但-你-\N{\fnArial\fs48}But you --
Dialogue: 100,0:09:02.04,0:09:03.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，现在没时间废话\N{\fnArial\fs48}ugh! There's no time for this.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:04.28,0:09:04.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}准备好了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ready?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:05.10,0:09:05.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}收起泡泡\N{\fnArial\fs48}Drop the bubble.
