Dialogue: 600,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.07,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}康妮用刀的招式与《剑风传奇》中的格斯类似
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.34,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}难怪它没有脉搏\N{\fnArial\fs48}So that's why it had no pulse.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.02,0:09:33.39,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}宝石人实验品\N{\fnArial\fs48}Gem experiments.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.96,0:09:35.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这就是你一直在做的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is what you've been doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.80,0:09:38.30,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}训练着与这些...东西战斗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Training to fight these...Things?
