Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对不起，莫雪伦医生\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sorry, Dr. Maheshwaren.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:41.98,0:09:42.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那是我的狮子\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's my Lion.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.56,0:09:47.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}妈妈，我很抱歉我对你撒谎了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mom, I'm really sorry about lying to you.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.82,0:09:49.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这一开始只是个小秘密\N{\fnArial\fs48}It started off as a tiny secret,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.04,0:09:52.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而我感觉如果我说出来\N{\fnArial\fs48}and then it felt like if I didn't hide it,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你不会再让我与史蒂文相处了\N{\fnArial\fs48}you wouldn't let me see Steven ever again.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:55.38,0:09:58.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这就是你的感受吗？我们是不是干预的太过了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is that how you feel? Are we too controlling?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}也许吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Maybe.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.56,0:10:02.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我只是想成为一个好母亲\N{\fnArial\fs48}I just wanted to be a good mother.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.28,0:10:04.78,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-我只是想保护你\N{\fnArial\fs48}I-I just wanted to protect you.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.66,0:10:07.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我现在可以保护自己了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can protect myself now.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.80,0:10:12.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.64,0:10:15.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们-会修改规矩的\N{\fnArial\fs48}We'll pull back on the rules,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.66,0:10:17.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而我会试着接受\N{\fnArial\fs48}and I'll try to keep an open mind
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.28,0:10:21.72,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这个，那个，和...他\N{\fnArial\fs48}about this and that and...Him.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.78,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我很害怕我没法和你沟通\N{\fnArial\fs48}It scares me that you can't talk to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.30,0:10:28.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我得知道你的生活是什么样的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I need to know what's happening in your life.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.78,0:10:31.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我得在你 时\N{\fnArial\fs48}I need to step in when you're in over your head.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.10,0:10:34.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你能对我保证你停止遮掩吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Will you just promise me you'll stop all this lying?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:36.42,0:10:37.34,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那是个规矩\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's a rule.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.56,0:10:39.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我爱你，亲爱的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I love you, honey.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:40.06,0:10:41.32,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我也爱你，妈妈\N{\fnArial\fs48}I love you too, mom.
Dialogue: 200,0:10:51.70,0:10:54.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn华文楷体\fs64}我认为我非常卑微\N{\fnArial\fs48}♪ I always thought I might be bad ♪
Dialogue: 200,0:10:54.66,0:10:57.34,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn华文楷体\fs64}现在我已确定\N{\fnArial\fs48}♪ now I'm sure that it's true
Dialogue: 200,0:10:57.70,0:11:00.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn华文楷体\fs64}因，你如此完美\N{\fnArial\fs48}♪ 'cause I think you're so good ♪
